    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 62-65.</p><p>Sneak Attack Master</p><p>When you reach 24th level, you can use your Sneak Attack one additional time per turn, as long as you meet its requirements. In addition, you can perform your Mortal Blow one additional time per round. Once you have performed 2 Mortal Blows, you cannot do so again until the start of your next turn.</p></div>",
